The damage caused by floods in Durban. DURBAN - Mop-up operations continue in KwaZulu-Natal. NGOs are lending a helping hand to residents who have lost so much. Meanwhile, water and electricity issues continue as schooling has also been interrupted. Mop-up operations continue in KZN. Water and electricity issues continue as schooling has also been interrupted. Courtesy #DStv403 eNCA reporter, Aviwe Mtila is on the ground with the latest.